Name: Dateline: Unforgettable
Title: After the Dance
Desc: The kidnapping and murder of Carla Walker following a Valentine's Day dance in Fort Worth, Texas.
LongDescription: Josh Mankiewicz re-examines the kidnapping and murder of 17-year-old Carla Walker following a Valentine's Day dance in Fort Worth, Texas; Cutting-edge DNA technology and diligent police work lead detectives to her killer.
